snippet.title: Saucy Boy Adventures - Full Gameplay Video
snippet.description:
FREE GAME DOWNLOAD: https://rhubarbzoo.itch.io/saucy-boy-adventures

SOUNDTRACK: https://danejacobs.bandcamp.com/album/saucy-boy-adventures-ost

Rhubarb Zoo has released their first game! It's a cute little shoot-em-up (or "cute-em-up") about a little flying saucer on a quest to retrieve three hotdog sauces.

Give it a shot! Let us know if you find any bugs!

If you can't play the game or if you just want to check out the animation, this video is a full play through from beginning to end.

Thanks for watching!
